Name: Eyeshadow Palette 28
Short description: An eyeshadow palette with 28 shades that beautifully layer together for breathtaking eye looks.
Description:
What it is:
An eyeshadow palette with 28 shades that beautifully layer together for breathtaking eye looks.

What it does:
Natasha Denona’s Eyeshadow Palette 28 is ultra-pigmented, blends like a dream, and is long lasting. Enriched with moisturizing ingredients, it’s made with real crushed pearls that create a radiant glow. The palette features an array of ultra-pigmented, unique shades and finishes. The revolutionary formula is smooth to the touch so that eye color glides seamlessly onto your lids while providing vivid color payoff with a silky-soft feel.

Each palette contains:
Purple Blue Palette:
- 28 x 0.08 oz/ 2.26 g Eyeshadow in Cool Plum (mocha with red undertones), Vintage (red-toned brown with shimmer), Oxide (intense copper), Golden Beige (peach with champagne glitter), Quick Silver (dark charcoal gray), Deep Pacific (deep blue green) Glaze (soft sand), Satin Skin (sand-toned shimmer), Smoky Plum (deep purple/burgundy undertone) Rosewood (chocolate shimmer/red undertone), Golden Rose (raspberry pink with gold iridescence), Steel Blue (gray), Powder Blue (turquoise), Gray-brown (milk chocolate), Lavender Gray (bronze/light copper undertone), Electric Violet (cool violet with blue undertones), Maroon (rich burgundy), Piggy (champagne shimmer/pink undertones), Metallic Steel Blue (deep blue), Petroleum Blue (intense electric aqua blue), Chromatic (intense silver), Deep Slate Gray (chocolate brown/charcoal undertone), Nina's Orchid (vivid fuchsia), Auvergne (blue), Calypso Blue (purple with blue shimmer), Smoke (charcoal gray), Koh Tao (powder blue), Navy (deep blue)

Green-Brown Palette:
- 28 x 0.08 oz/ 2.26 g Eyeshadow in Suede (soft brown with gold shimmer), Indian Gold (fine sand shimmer), Industrial (intense taupe shimmer), Smoky Quartz (chocolate brown shimmer), Antique Olive (deep gold/green undertones), Sand Storm (matte burnt orange), Ochre (bronze shimmer/brown undertones), Skin (rose shimmer/pink undertones), Moonstone (champagne shimmer/peach undertone), Aluminum (vibrant metallic silver), True Gold (intense metallic gold), Pinija (moss green shimmer/brown undertones), Terracotta (rich copper), Sienna (metallic bronze/copper undertones), Shell (matte rose) Cream (creamy white/light iridescence), Golden Aquamarine (mint green with a silver pearlescent), Glam Green (taupe shimmer/green undertones), Bottle Green (deep green with gold), Arizona (matte terracotta), Golden Flesh (bronzed gold/copper undertones), Umber (burnt orange/brown undertones), Flamingo (matte peach-toned pink), Tropic (aqua with pearlescent gold), Cloudy Blue (ocean blue with a gold shimmer), Emerald Green (jade green), Cool Bronze (bronze/burnt orange undertone), Satin Tan (sand with subtle gold shimmer)

Each palette is sold separately.

What it is formulated WITHOUT:
- Parabens
- Sulfates
- Phthalates

What else you need to know:
Internationally renowned makeup artist Natasha Denona developed her own eyeshadow formulas after struggling for over 20 years with eyeshadows that were dry, dull, and difficult to blend.

"When I launched these palettes everyone told me I was crazy because there are so many shades inside. I made them like this because I had to create a kit with all the basic colors that came in cool tones and warm tones from light to dark and in several textures. My 28 Palettes have become world renowned and the favorites of Desi Perkins, Nikki Tutorials, Wayne Goss, Kathleen Lights, and Jaclyn Hill. The formula is out of this world! It was a dream for me to create a pressed pigment that was easy for everyone to use. You can create endless looks with the 28 Palette. It’s a revolutionary product and a must have for everyone."—Natasha Denona

This product is cruelty-free.

Clean at Sephora
When you spot our Clean seal, you can be sure we’ve checked that this brand’s product is made without the ingredients you told us you’d most like to avoid.

Finish your look and let it stand out by layering a bright color or lamé pop on top.

Read the shade names from left to right for a short poem. The slim, seven-shadow palette was designed to feature the oblong infinity mirror, and was inspired by the rearview mirror of an automobile.

Each palette features its own shade personality:
Provocouture (dusty plum and magenta): Say it with style; otherwise, you might as well just stay in bed.
Glambition (bare and bronze): She was infamous, known for seeking the most over-the-top glamour.
Frivoluxe (chilled greige and violet): Fabulous! Always dress outrageously and how you want. Who has time for less?
Scandalust (rust and warmed browns with scarlet): Hot pants at the office cause a fuss; that’s why they call her little miss scandalous.
Edgitorial (camouflage and reflective gold): Take a memo. Next season, we’ll see, pleather python, making a scene, enviously, everywhere.
Sartorial (celestial cobalt and icy teal with prismatic gray): Whenever in doubt: power platforms. Make sure (for once) they know who runs the show.

What else you need to know:
"I wanted to make getting the ultimate glow easy for everyone. So we combined colors, formula and technique to make highlighting like a pro within each person’s grasp. Highlighter can really magnify any makeup, but there are concerns for people with larger pores as the pigments tend to emphasize skin unevenness which is a problem that I have. I love to blend face oils and pigments together to smooth the skin texture and amplify the reflection of the pearls. That’s when I knew I had to create this highlighter. 20 Very Fair: Mauve brightens sallowness. Light yellow neutralizes redness.
 
25 Light: Light green corrects redness. Light peach brightens the under-eye area.

30 Medium: Olive green corrects overall redness and blemishes. Peach corrects dark circles.

40 Tan: Dark peach counteracts dark circles with blue undertones. Yellow ochre evens out by correcting overall redness in skin tone.

50 Dark: Brick corrects deep hyperpigmentation. Caramel neutralizes dark spots for an even complexion.

55 Deep: Orange corrects hyperpigmentation under eyes or face. Dark brown deepens lighter areas of the skin.
Attribute 1 value(s): 20 very fair,25 light,30 medium,40 tan,50 dark,55 deep

beautyblender's unique material is aqua-activated™. When wet, it expands to about twice its size and becomes super soft to create an even, smooth blend and bounce, returning to its original size when it air dries. It is handcrafted in the USA.

beautyblender has chosen to use non-toxic, water-soluble dyes. For this reason, your beautyblender may shed dye for the first couple of washes—similar to a pair of blue jeans. Name: Empty Shade + Light Crème Contour Palette
Short description: An empty palette with six magnetic wells, designed to store three highlight and three contour shades for a completely customizable contour experience.
Description:
To redeem your set:
1. SELECT the Customizable Contour Palette.
2. SELECT any three highlight refills and any three contour refills in the shades of your choice.
3. ADD EACH ITEM TO BASKET.
4. GET A DEAL: Discount will be applied at checkout. Your final set will be $49 for US clients ($101 value), and C$64 for Canadian clients (a C$131 value).

Note: Each item will display separately with the original price when added to your basket. The discount will display above your order total. Additional promotions and discount offers do not apply to this set.

What it is:
An empty palette with six magnetic wells, designed to store three highlight and three contour shades for a completely customizable contour experience.

What it does:
By popular demand, Kat Von D created a completely customizable version of her iconic Shade + Light Face Contour Palette. The Shade + Light Customizable Contour Palette features the same sleek, hard-shell case as the original bestselling palette, with six empty magnetic wells—thee for highlight shades and three for contour shades.

For the first time ever, you have the opportunity to select the shades, formulas and format of your contour palette. Powder or crème? Shadowplay or Sombre? The Shade + Light Customizable Contour Palette puts you in charge, for endless combinations and looks.

What else you need to know:
To refill or remove pans, insert a pin into the hole on the back of the palette.

"The true inspiration behind the Shade + Light Contour Palette comes from all these years of trying to understand the usage of shadows and light within the portraits I draw."—Kat Von D, Brand Founder

All Kat Von D products are vegan and cruelty-free.
